title: AtmosFEARfx - Ghostly Apparitions (Halloween Visual Effects)
description:
About AtmosFEARfx
Use your TV, monitor or projector to display AtmosFEARfx digital decorations and turn any environment or surface into a thrilling, haunting experience. Perfect for Halloween decorating, trick-or-treaters, parties and more.

About Ghostly Apparitions
Transform any environment into a haunted house with this ghoulish gathering of spooky specters! Ghostly Apparitions allows you to create the ultimate ghost hunting experience by providing a collection of restless spirits that are simply dying to inhabit your home
